Create Flex Prompt Templates with Free Text Inputs

Enjoy more powerful customization capabilities for your prompt authoring. Prompt Builder now supports free text inputs for use in flex prompt templates, so you can now use flex prompt templates in scenarios when you want to provide any manner of text as an input to your prompt.

This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions. Einstein generative AI is available in Lightning Experience.

Starting on June 26, 2024.
